Title: Vortex Line Nucleation of First-Order Transition U(1)-Symmetric Field
  Systems
Author: H. Kleinert
Comments: Author Information under
  http://www.physik.fu-berlin.de/~kleinert/institution.html . Latest update of
  paper also at
  http://www.physik.fu-berlin.de/~kleinert/kleiner_re278/preprint.html
Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B460 (1999) 36-40
\\
  We show that in field systems with U(1)-symmetry, first-order transitions are
nucleated by vortex lines, not bubbles, thus calling for a reinvestigation of
the Kibble mechanism for the phase transition of the early universe.
\\
